Subscribers are organized in categories, thus we allow you to create such a hierarchy of cateogries using this form. You
can go as deep as you like, but be warned that displaying a tree that get's too deep can cause problems. Keep a balance between the
unlimited power we give you and the limitations of your choosen design ... Also, this list of 'categories' will be shown to the user
so he can select which kind of mailing he wants to receive ...